Local modifications by this repo:
  - Hardcoded `node .claude/skills/impeccable/scripts/...` paths rewritten to
    `node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/skills/impeccable/scripts/...` so the bundled
    scripts resolve when loaded as a Claude Code plugin.
  - SKILL.md allowed-tools extended to permit the bundled node scripts.

To update: re-pull upstream's `plugin/` directory and re-apply the two
modifications above (the path rewrite is mechanical:
`.claude/skills/impeccable/scripts` -> `${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/skills/impeccable/scripts`).
